<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <title>Hello, world!</title>
    <style>
        .content {
            width: 50%;
           margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .content form{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .content form input{
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .btn button{
            width: 30%;
            border:  1px solid black;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: transparent;
            box-shadow: 0px 1px 5px 0px #888888;
        }
        .btn button:hover{
            width: 30%;
            border:  1px solid black;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0px 1px 5px 0px #888888;
        }
        .right {
            margin-top: 20px;
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .item{
            width: 60%;
        }
        .content1 {
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
        }

        .image {
            opacity: 1;
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            transition: .5s ease;
        }

        .middle {
            transition: .5s ease;
            opacity: 0;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content1:hover .image {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .content1:hover .middle {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        .tag {
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
        }

        .tag p {
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .tag p:hover {
            font-size: 14px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .titleNoiDung {
            cursor: pointer;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 1;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 18px
        }

        .titleNoiDung:hover {
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #00B7FF;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 1;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .date {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
        }

        .share {
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #696666
        }

        .share:hover {
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #00B7FF;
        }

        #box {
            padding-top: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            height: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0px 1px 7px 0px #888888;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .item:hover #box {
            padding-top: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            height: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0px 1px 10px 0px #888888;
        }
        .footer{
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-left: 10px;
            color: #00B7FF;

        }
        .footer:hover{
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-left: 10px;
            color: #00B7FF;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="container-full">
<% include nav.ejs %>
<div class="container-full" style="background: #efeded;">
    <div class="container" style="display: flex;flex-direction: row;height: auto">
        <div class="content">
            <form action="/updateHinhNen" method="post" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded">
                <input name="id" type="hidden" value="<%= data._id %>">
                <input name="noiDung" required placeholder="Nhập nội dung" value="<%= data.noiDung %>">
                <input type="date" name="ngayThang" required placeholder="Nhập ngày tháng" value="<%= data.ngayThang %>">
                <input name="linkAnh" required placeholder="Nhập link ảnh" value="<%= data.linkAnh %>">
                <div class="btn">
                    <button type="submit" name="update">Update</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
            <div class="item">
                <div class="content1">
                    <img src="<%= data.linkAnh %>" alt="Avatar" class="image"
                         style="width:100%;height: 600px">
                    <div class="middle">
                        <form method="post" action="/showdetail">
                            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= data._id %>">
                            <button style="background-color: transparent;border: none">
                                <img src="images/image.png" width="60px" height="60px">
                            </button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="box" class="container" style="background-color:white">
                    <div class="tag">
                        <img src="https://img.icons8.com/plumpy/344/tag.png" width="20" height="20">
                        <p style="margin-left: 10px; color: #00B7FF;">#Hình nền động</p>
                        <p>,</p>
                        <p style="margin-left: 10px; color: #00B7FF;">#Ngầu</p>
                    </div>
                    <form method="post" action="/showdetail">
                        <button style="border: none;width: 300px;background-color: transparent">
                            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= data._id %>">
                            <h4 style="padding-top: 10px;transition: .3s ease"
                                class="titleNoiDung"><%= data.noiDung %></h4>
                        </button>
                    </form>

                    <p style="padding-top: 10px;overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;display: -webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp: 4;-webkit-box-orient: vertical;color: #888888"><%= data.noiDung %>
                        . Bạn rất thích trang trí cho dế yêu của bạn ? Trang web này sẽ luôn cung cấp cho các bạn
                        những hình nền điện thoại đẹp và theo xu hướng mới nhất. Hình nền điện thoại được lựa chọn
                        từ nhiều
                        nguồn khác nhau và chọn lọc kĩ càng với chất lượng tốt nhất.</p>
                    <div class="date">
                        <img src="images/date.png" width="15px" height="15px">
                        <p style="font-size: 12px;color: #696666;margin-left: 10px"><%= data.ngayThang %></p>
                        <img src="images/share.png" width="17px" height="17px" style="margin-left: 10px">
                        <p class="share" style="margin-left: 10px">Share</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-full" style="background-color: white;height: 250px;margin-top: 30px;">
    <div style="display: flex;flex-direction: row;padding-top: 150px;padding-left: 200px">
        <div>POWER BY</div>
        <a style=" text-decoration: none;" href="http://localhost:3000/">
            <div class="footer" >HÌNH NỀN ĐIỆN THOẠI ĐẸP</div>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>


